## Out of scope (explicitly not v1)
- Authentication / authorization, multi-tenancy, offline support.
- LLM/AI features (workflow's Gemini layer is N/A for this project — see decisions.mdc).
- Cloud hosting (all-local Docker Compose — see decisions.mdc).
- Order editing, cancellation-after-confirm, returns, partial fulfillment.
